---
import MinimalLayout from '@layouts/MinimalLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '@components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import ZcalWidget from '@components/ZcalWidget.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/blog' },
  { label: 'Vana Case Study' }
];

const title = "How Vana Cut Collection Costs by 70% with AI - Kleva Blog";
const description = "Case study: How a Guatemala microlender transformed their collections with Kleva's AI agents, reducing costs by 70% while increasing recovery rates.";
---

<MinimalLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="blog-post">
    <div class="container">
      <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbs} />
      
      <header class="post-header">
        <div class="post-meta">
          <span class="category">Case Study</span>
          <span class="date">November 5, 2024</span>
          <span class="read-time">6 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1>How Vana Cut Collection Costs by 70% with AI</h1>
        <p class="post-excerpt">
          Case study: How a Guatemala microlender transformed their collections with Kleva's 
          AI agents, achieving remarkable results in just 90 days.
        </p>
        <div class="author-info">
          <span class="author">By Juli, Customer Success at Kleva</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="post-content">
        <section class="case-overview">
          <div class="company-info">
            <h2>About Vana</h2>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Industry:</strong> Microfinance</li>
              <li><strong>Location:</strong> Guatemala City, Guatemala</li>
              <li><strong>Portfolio:</strong> 45,000+ active loans</li>
              <li><strong>Average loan size:</strong> $850 USD</li>
              <li><strong>Challenge:</strong> 31% delinquency rate, rising operational costs</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>The Challenge: Collections Crisis</h2>
          <p>
            In early 2024, Vana faced a perfect storm:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Delinquency rates jumped from 18% to 31% in 6 months</li>
            <li>Collection costs exceeded $85 per recovered loan</li>
            <li>Agent turnover hit 120% annually</li>
            <li>Recovery rates dropped to 22%</li>
            <li>Customer complaints about aggressive collectors increased 3x</li>
          </ul>
          
          <blockquote>
            "We were hemorrhaging money. Every dollar we collected cost us $1.20. We were 
            literally paying to collect our own money."
            <cite>— Carlos Mendez, CFO of Vana</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>The Manual Operation: Unsustainable</h2>
          <div class="before-state">
            <h3>Vana's Collections Team (Before Kleva):</h3>
            <table>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td><strong>Team size:</strong></td>
                  <td>35 agents + 5 supervisors</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><strong>Monthly cost:</strong></td>
                  <td>$78,000 USD</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><strong>Calls per day:</strong></td>
                  <td>2,800 (80 per agent)</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><strong>Contact rate:</strong></td>
                  <td>12%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><strong>Promise to pay:</strong></td>
                  <td>18%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td><strong>Actual payment:</strong></td>
                  <td>7%</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          
          <p>
            The math was brutal: To collect $100,000 monthly, Vana spent $120,000 on operations.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>The Solution: Kleva AI Implementation</h2>
          
          <h3>Phase 1: Pilot Program (Week 1-2)</h3>
          <p>
            We started with 1,000 accounts to prove the concept:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Deployed 5 AI agents handling Guatemalan Spanish</li>
            <li>Integrated with Vana's loan management system</li>
            <li>Set up compliance rules for Guatemala regulations</li>
            <li>Configured payment collection via multiple channels</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>Phase 2: Rapid Scaling (Week 3-8)</h3>
          <p>
            After seeing 43% better results in the pilot:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Scaled to 15,000 delinquent accounts</li>
            <li>AI agents made 8,000+ calls daily</li>
            <li>Added WhatsApp and SMS follow-ups</li>
            <li>Implemented smart scheduling based on contact patterns</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>Phase 3: Full Deployment (Week 9-12)</h3>
          <p>
            Complete transformation of collections:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>AI handling 100% of first-contact attempts</li>
            <li>Human agents focused on complex negotiations</li>
            <li>24/7 operations (customers could pay anytime)</li>
            <li>Real-time performance optimization</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>The Results: Transformation in 90 Days</h2>
          
          <div class="results-comparison">
            <div class="metric-card before">
              <h3>Before Kleva</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Monthly cost: <span class="number">$78,000</span></li>
                <li>Recovery rate: <span class="number">22%</span></li>
                <li>Cost per dollar: <span class="number">$1.20</span></li>
                <li>Delinquency: <span class="number">31%</span></li>
                <li>Team size: <span class="number">40 people</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="metric-card after">
              <h3>After Kleva</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Monthly cost: <span class="number">$23,400</span></li>
                <li>Recovery rate: <span class="number">41%</span></li>
                <li>Cost per dollar: <span class="number">$0.35</span></li>
                <li>Delinquency: <span class="number">19%</span></li>
                <li>Team size: <span class="number">8 people</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="impact-summary">
            <div class="impact-item">
              <span class="impact-number">70%</span>
              <span class="impact-label">Cost Reduction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="impact-item">
              <span class="impact-number">86%</span>
              <span class="impact-label">Higher Recovery</span>
            </div>
            <div class="impact-item">
              <span class="impact-number">$650K</span>
              <span class="impact-label">Annual Savings</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Unexpected Benefits</h2>
          
          <h3>1. Customer Satisfaction Increased</h3>
          <blockquote>
            "Our NPS score went from -12 to +28. Customers actually thank us for the 
            respectful collection calls now."
            <cite>— Maria Lopez, Customer Experience Manager</cite>
          </blockquote>
          
          <h3>2. Employee Morale Improved</h3>
          <p>
            The 8 remaining human agents now handle complex cases and payment arrangements. 
            They're problem-solvers, not call-center workers. Turnover dropped to zero.
          </p>
          
          <h3>3. Data-Driven Insights</h3>
          <p>
            Kleva's analytics revealed patterns Vana never knew:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Best contact time: 7-9pm (not business hours)</li>
            <li>Optimal payment plan: 3 installments over 45 days</li>
            <li>Key predictor of payment: Answering within 3 rings</li>
            <li>Most effective opening: Mentioning loan purpose, not amount</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>4. Compliance Perfection</h3>
          <p>
            Zero regulatory violations since implementation. Every call is recorded, 
            transcribed, and automatically checked for compliance.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>ROI Analysis</h2>
          
          <div class="roi-breakdown">
            <h3>Investment</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Kleva setup fee: $15,000</li>
              <li>Monthly subscription: $8,400</li>
              <li>Integration costs: $5,000</li>
              <li><strong>Total Year 1: $115,800</strong></li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Savings</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Reduced labor costs: $54,600/month</li>
              <li>Increased recovery: $45,000/month</li>
              <li>Reduced compliance fines: $8,000/month</li>
              <li><strong>Total Year 1: $1,291,200</strong></li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="roi-result">
              <span class="roi-number">1,015%</span>
              <span class="roi-label">First Year ROI</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>What's Next for Vana</h2>
          <p>
            Encouraged by the results, Vana is expanding Kleva's role:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Proactive outreach:</strong> Contacting customers before they miss payments</li>
            <li><strong>Customer service:</strong> AI handling payment questions and loan inquiries</li>
            <li><strong>Loan origination:</strong> Initial screening and documentation collection</li>
            <li><strong>Regional expansion:</strong> Opening operations in Honduras and El Salvador</li>
          </ul>
          
          <blockquote>
            "Kleva didn't just solve our collections problem. It transformed our entire 
            business model. We're now a tech-forward lender that happens to be in Guatemala, 
            not a Guatemalan lender trying to use tech."
            <cite>— Roberto Vega, CEO of Vana</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>
          <ol>
            <li><strong>Speed matters:</strong> Full transformation in 90 days, ROI in 45 days</li>
            <li><strong>Culture fit is crucial:</strong> AI must speak local Spanish perfectly</li>
            <li><strong>Hybrid is best:</strong> AI + humans outperforms either alone</li>
            <li><strong>Data drives success:</strong> Insights from AI calls improved overall strategy</li>
            <li><strong>Compliance is non-negotiable:</strong> Perfect regulatory adherence is possible</li>
          </ol>
        </section>

        <div class="post-cta">
          <h3>Transform Your Collections Like Vana</h3>
          <p>
            See how Kleva can reduce your collection costs by 70% while improving recovery rates.
          </p>
          <ZcalWidget mode="popup" buttonText="Get your custom ROI analysis" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</MinimalLayout>

<style>
  .blog-post {
    padding: 120px 0 80px;
  }

  .post-header {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .post-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  .category {
    color: var(--color-black);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--color-black);
  }

  .post-excerpt {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .author-info {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
  }

  .post-content {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .post-content section {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .post-content h2 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--color-black);
  }

  .post-content h3 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 32px 0 16px;
    color: var(--color-black);
  }

  .post-content p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
  }

  .post-content ul, .post-content ol {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  .post-content li {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
  }

  .company-info {
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .company-info h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .before-state {
    background: #fff5f5;
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 2px solid #ff0000;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .before-state h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: #cc0000;
  }

  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
  }

  td {
    padding: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  td:first-child {
    font-weight: 600;
    width: 40%;
  }

  .results-comparison {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .metric-card {
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .metric-card.before {
    background: #fff5f5;
    border: 2px solid #ff0000;
  }

  .metric-card.after {
    background: #f0fff0;
    border: 2px solid #00cc00;
  }

  .metric-card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .metric-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .metric-card li {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .number {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .impact-summary {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .impact-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 24px;
    background: var(--color-black);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .impact-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .impact-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-gray-300);
  }

  blockquote {
    margin: 32px 0;
    padding: 24px;
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-black);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .roi-breakdown {
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .roi-breakdown h3 {
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .roi-breakdown h3:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .roi-result {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding: 24px;
    background: var(--color-black);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .roi-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .roi-label {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-gray-300);
  }

  .post-cta {
    margin-top: 64px;
    padding: 48px;
    background: var(--color-black);
    border-radius: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .post-cta h3 {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .post-cta p {
    color: var(--color-gray-300);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
    }

    .results-comparison,
    .impact-summary {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .post-meta {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }
  }
</style>